# Build Bible V2 — Chapter 4 (Design System)

Spec: `docs/06_BUILD_BIBLE_V2_CHAPTER_04_DESIGN_SYSTEM.md`

## Sources of truth

- Tokens: `src/app/globals.css`, `src/lib/ui/tokens.ts`, `src/lib/ui/form-tokens.ts`, `src/lib/ui/aurora.ts`
- Components: `src/components/ui/**` — one primitive per concern

## Rules

- Merge duplicate UI; do not create parallel buttons/cards/tables/badges/empty states.
- Prefer semantic color/spacing tokens over one-off class strings.
- Forms: shared field components + `form-tokens` label/helper/error patterns.
- Tables: `AuroraTable*` / `DataTableShell`.
- Loading/empty: `EmptyState`, `Skeleton`, `RouteLoadingShell`, `LoadingCard`.
- Keep focus rings and accessible interactive states.
- Presentation only — never change auth, RBAC, RLS, or Paddle billing behaviour.

## This chapter

- Do not commit, push, or deploy from Chapter 4 work.
